reviews.text:
This is an awesomely unique cereal. I review it on my video "This Week with Wayne: 09-07-2017". I can easily see how it was inspired by Lucky Bird, but it's not the same flavor at all. There's more a focus on the sweet marshmallows and milk, with a touch of this unique cereal note that follows the vape. Upon looking at the recipe, I didn't expect it to come out this good and this focused. All these creams and dairy accents seemed like it would be muddled, but it comes out with an awesome flavor that's so much smoother than Lucky Bird, and much more flavorful. I do think there is room for consolidation or subtraction, to help focus the recipe even more. I'm happy with the result, though, and will def finish this bottle soon. &#xD;
&#xD;
EDIT: The version I mixed did not have FW Hazelnut.
